TextBody:
Hello Florian,

There is an issue on our side and the patch still appears as available even after applying it.
You can verify if the patch was correctly applied accessing Dashboard -> Live update -> View Applied EPP Software Updates.
If the Server update appears in this list, then you should not worry about the patch. It will automatically disappear from the available patches soon.

Best regards,
Emil
